➜省联社淄博审计中心与桓台农商银行召开“绿能贷”信贷产品发布会
http://www.sohu.com/a/415767068_100198835	30056
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200831/54a234fb85b64ce2acb25805c6bf3fbf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200831/51c94c49da2a4b23a7f4a87fb6a7e87a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200831/7337b939b7d24b3cadb9e36bf27bf6c7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200831/b6676110aeac4a60bf86b9e4eeb4b6ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
